title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Aug 19 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Aug 19 2022
description:
A fired-up Donald Trump Jr. joins Clay and Buck to discuss his family's reaction to the raid at Mar-a-Lago. He says, "They're trying to disqualify their biggest threat." Don Jr. also talks with C&B about how to push back against the Deep State and who from the "amazingly deep" Democrat bench will get the 2024 nomination? Which is the most incompetent three-letter agency in the government: IRS, FBI, or CDC? Will there be consequence for the people who got covid wrong? CDC’s Walensky makes excuses for all the mistakes and lies. Clay reads a heartbreaking VIP Email from the wife of a covid victim.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
